sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Students Import Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open students import page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW-->>UI: Render CSV upload form

    User->>UI: Upload CSV and start import
    UI->>LW: import()
    LW->>LW: Validate file and CSV headers
    alt Invalid file/header
        LW-->>UI: Error toast
    else Valid CSV
        loop For each row
            LW->>DB: Validate row and run transaction (create user/student + sync classes)
            alt Row valid
                DB-->>LW: Row imported
            else Row invalid/conflict
                DB-->>LW: Validation error
            end
        end
        LW-->>UI: Show summary logs (processed/imported/skipped)
    end
